<h2 align="center">Wedding Dinner Planning System</h2>
<h3 align="left">Introduction to Application</h3>
<p align="left">The Wedding Dinner Planning System is a 
web-based application, which is used by agencies to book restaurant dinners and 
arranging guest seating plan for their customers. The application was built by 
using Java Servlet / JSP technology and running on Apache Tomcat Web Server and 
MySQL Database Management System.</p>
<p align="left">Below shows a list of basic functionalities 
that has been realized:</p>
<ol>
  <li>
<div align="left">Create / update / delete weddings</div>
  <li>
<div align="left">Create / update / delete guests for weddings</div>
  <li>
<div align="left">Create guests for weddings (using batch uploading mode)</div>
  <li>
<div align="left">Assign guests to tables</div>
  <li>
<div align="left">View guest status</div>
  <li>
<div align="left">Mark guest attendance</div>
  <li>
<div align="left"> Generate reports</div></li></ol>
<h3 align="left"> Innovative Features</h3>
<p align="left">Below shows a list of innovative features for the system</p>
<ol>
  <li>
<div align="left">Support multiple hotels / restaurants book service</div>
  <li>
<div align="left">Support 2 modes of table assignment 
  (manual mode and auto mode)</div>
  <li>
<div align="left">Support 2 formats of report generation 
  (PDF format and Microsoft Excel Sheet format)</div></li></ol>
